OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening for most with some late sunny
OL,7,Fspells, though one or two light
OL,8,Fshowers are possible. Turning damp
OL,9,Fovernight with some rain for many, but
OL,10,Fthis mostly light. Freshening
OL,11,Fsoutheasterly winds and turning rather
OL,12,Fwindy in places. Mild.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FA damp morning with rain and
OL,15,Fdrizzle at times, but also some drier
OL,16,Fperiods. Further showers are possible
OL,17,Fduring the afternoon, these probably
OL,18,Fheavier, with hail and thunder
OL,19,Fpossible. Cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
