OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fand windy on Sunday with rain at
OL,7,Ftimes, perhaps heavy over Cumbria and
OL,8,Fmore widely later. Rain clearing to
OL,9,Fsunny spells on Monday. Sunshine and
OL,10,Fblustery showers on Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
